summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 74W, page 175 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle (Ordinance 86300) to rezone certain property located approximately 66 feet south of South Othello Street and 179 feet east of Rainier Avenue South from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone.
